item.why: Neil's Donuts opened in June 2001 and ever since they have been selling the most delicious donuts in Southern CT. We can meet there, (Closes @ 1p Sun.) buy some donuts and coffee and then go to Community Lake Park which is down the road on route 150.
item.name: Let's meet at Neil's Donuts in Wallingford and then go to Community Lake Park
